                        <div class="team-details__content">
                            <h2>Kawser Ahmed</h2>
                            <span>Web Design</span>
                            <p class="mt-25">Adipiscing elit. Mauris viverra nisl quis mollis laoreet. Ut eget lacus
                                a felis
                                accumsan
                                pharetra in dignissim enim. In
                                amet odio mollis urna aliquet volutpat. Sed bibendum nisl vehicula imperdiet
                                imperdiet,
                                augue massa fringilla.</p>
                            <ul class="bor-top bor-bottom pt-30 pb-30">
                                <li>Experiencia: 10 anos</li>
                                <li>
